data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Boasting a beautiful oversized CORNER LOT, 2444 SqFt of spacious living space and vinyl privacy fence. This lovely home offers the financial benefit of an ASSUMABLE VA LOAN. The interior is just as appealing, with plenty of storage, additional loft space, and a downstair bedroom with designated full bath - perfect for visitors. This home features tile flooring throughout the main floor, high ceilings throughout, security camera connection, and Phonyx Smart System. The HVAC system is designed for comfort with one unit equipped with 2 SEPARATE THERMOSTATS. The kitchen is open with plenty of lower and 42” upper cabinets with crown molding, Recess Can lighting, Quartz counters top, island breakfast bar, pantry, and matching stainless steel appliance package with Wi-Fi Connect built-in microwave/oven, and separate gas cooktop. Additionally, separate laundry room connected to the garage, laundry tub pre-plumb at the garage and water softener connection. Upstairs relax in the spacious owner's suite featuring Tray ceiling, oversized walk-in closet, double vanity, and spacious walk-in shower stall. The secondary bedrooms feature a dual sink and private shower room. The outside space features a covered lanai with gas connection for a BBQ kitchen, tankless water heater, and spacious maintained yard with plenty space to build your dream pool, the possibilities are endless! Located in the highly coveted community of MiraBay, enjoy all the neighborhood has to offer including community pool, playground, rec center, basketball, tennis courts, summer & fall camp, after daycare service, all within 4 minutes’ walk, and so much more! Don't miss this excellent opportunity!
